opa幫我清左好多關於3D嘅concept,如果冇佢我一定冇lv5&amp;nbsp;<br />\n另外,我有Koopa $200學券有冇興趣收左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個底邊會有5**<br />\nLQ一條都唔識做"},{"pid":"8bd8a7a33d46a09c57fce7634f5e9e38d169492b","tid":379774,"uid":141616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋我唔建議樓主aim level4 <br />\n<br />\n因為通常aim 4嘅人最後出到嚟成績都會得3<br />\n<br />\n其實dick hui都唔一定for 補底嘅<br />\n<br />\nf5個時補過佢一期<br />\n<br />\n佢份notes入面都有啲幾難嘅問題可以做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\naim level5 嘅人都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有乜見意？"},{"pid":"861c47fc5d3ba077faca0397e78527996745bcb3","tid":379774,"uid":141616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而且我好想知道樓主中幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中六啦<br />\n最後7個月啦"},{"pid":"303dcac1b520cfbc5ce44f6d57bbda25680bfe0a","tid":379774,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而且我好想知道樓主中幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中六啦<br />\n最後7個月啦</blockquote><br />\n你有冇做過past paper<br />\nA1 A2岩幾多/識唔識做<br />\nMC岩幾多/識唔識做"},{"pid":"eff08cf843f433f49c1758372e2b553db1b11df7","tid":379774,"uid":133877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"Herman Yeung啦,唔洗錢又高質,仲可以重睇無限次"},{"pid":"a40436782f6ad158e393bf1375e91432fdd2fa3f","tid":379774,"uid":133877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Herman Yeung啦,唔洗錢又高質,仲可以重睇無限次</blockquote><br />\n利申:中五開始無番學全自修<br />\nCore M2 5"},{"pid":"3e07f7cb1b1f0ef9d98bc06146ec2f0845c62642","tid":379774,"uid":137912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:17:44.000Z","msg":"個post好多hy打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a49150a0c3411a43fc9b8bc2aeb1a23b3f1fac0","tid":379774,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"正正常常<br />\n有少少logic都拎到4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7027528de6cc6911be66926abe8ab43fdf386d2","tid":379774,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post好多hy打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 上連登 梗係HY啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:打手"},{"pid":"88e8caf2494486e5745234c8fcb403d2b993595c","tid":379774,"uid":129850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"Herman yeung d 片係好既<br />\n解得幾清晰<br />\n<br />\n不過，補習，要成套野齊，包埋 notes <br />\n<br />\n同埋，出去補，有個進度去跟，係有效 D 既"},{"pid":"3cd555ea673535bb14194c1360b9ac69960f22b5","tid":379774,"uid":127141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"4 係好易拎<br />\n<br />\n但要升上 5 up<br />\n就真係要操得熟 D<br />\n<br />\n因為 4 個 range 其實好大<br />\n<br />\n而且上年 17 DSE ，著重左考數底。<br />\n好多補習佬教既 skill 都未必全部用得著"},{"pid":"7460296e886783b9aae25f4f188f1c72bbc8c021","tid":379774,"uid":133877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Herman yeung d 片係好既<br />\n解得幾清晰<br />\n<br />\n不過，補習，要成套野齊，包埋 notes <br />\n<br />\n同埋，出去補，有個進度去跟，係有效 D 既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHerman Yeung 都有個十五日完成DSE Core既課程<br />\n仲有心整埋2002-2017 Past paper solution<br />\n有需要咪睇下囉<br />\n缺點:屋企可能專心唔到<br />\n<br />\ndick hui或者herman yeung等人唔似得某燈塔老師剩係教神技<br />\n比你大學入到Science/Engine甚至Econ都會跟唔上<br />\n<br />\n大班補習一大缺點就係學生能力差距問題<br />\n講得太快又跟唔上,講得太慢又嫌晒時間晒錢<br />\n萬一真係跟唔上而報VIP,原因係為左按pause,<br />\n其實網上仲有好多其他資源,都可以比你慢慢學習<br />\nkhan academy係一個外國既網頁<br />\n包含maths,science,computing,econ等等<br />\n<br />\n總結如果格硬揀,我會dick hui/私補"},{"pid":"62ca816f79e2e81d51361b0f591bb68c8e76a5c6","tid":379774,"uid":141616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4 係好易拎<br />\n<br />\n但要升上 5 up<br />\n就真係要操得熟 D<br />\n<br />\n因為 4 個 range 其實好大<br />\n<br />\n而且上年 17 DSE ，著重左考數底。<br />\n好多補習佬教既 skill 都未必全部用得著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有乜高見<br />\n邊個OK呀"},{"pid":"f623a1ad80fec9de356936d417aa80d749f4da2d","tid":379774,"uid":141616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Herman yeung d 片係好既<br />\n解得幾清晰<br />\n<br />\n不過，補習，要成套野齊，包埋 notes <br />\n<br />\n同埋，出去補，有個進度去跟，係有效 D 既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHerman Yeung 都有個十五日完成DSE Core既課程<br />\n仲有心整埋2002-2017 Past paper solution<br />\n有需要咪睇下囉<br />\n缺點:屋企可能專心唔到<br />\n<br />\ndick hui或者herman yeung等人唔似得某燈塔老師剩係教神技<br />\n比你大學入到Science/Engine甚至Econ都會跟唔上<br />\n<br />\n大班補習一大缺點就係學生能力差距問題<br />\n講得太快又跟唔上,講得太慢又嫌晒時間晒錢<br />\n萬一真係跟唔上而報VIP,原因係為左按pause,<br />\n其實網上仲有好多其他資源,都可以比你慢慢學習<br />\nkhan academy係一個外國既網頁<br />\n包含maths,science,computing,econ等等<br />\n<br />\n總結如果格硬揀,我會dick hui/私補</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補得dick 就唔私補啦<br />\n邊有咁多錢"},{"pid":"ac0c11ceab3a4554991332b24c70435669da9fa5","tid":379774,"uid":129850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"Dick hui 好似好多學生"},{"pid":"b1f1e4f38564647df65494a7bf0caf7a383ba229","tid":379774,"uid":141616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dick hui 好似好多學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多真係唔代表好"},{"pid":"3a0f85451ba833453bdf4dc664c484d62d3c41fb","tid":379774,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15